articles.title: Fragile ceasefire appears to hold between Iran and Israel as Trump vents frustration with both sides.
articles.description: A fragile ceasefire between Iran and Israel appeared to be holding after initially faltering. U.S. President Donald Trump expressed frustration with both sides.
